## How to Read This Changelog

- **Version N** — A snapshot of the rubric at that point in time.
- **Trigger** — What caused the rubric to evolve:
  - `initial` — First-ever rubric generation
  - `periodic` — Scheduled evolution (every N evals)
  - `plateau` — Score stagnation triggered re-evaluation
- **Active Criteria** — Currently used for scoring.
- **Retired Criteria** — No longer scored but preserved for history.

